Package: CoDaStereo
Title: Compositional Data Analysis for Stereological and Histomorphometric Data
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: person("Diogo B.", "Provete", email = "diogo.provete@ufms.br",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1981-8865"))
Description: Shiny application implementing the Aitchison geometry for
    stereological and histomorphometric data. Covers the full PPDAC cycle:
    data upload, zero/NA handling, compositional visualisation (ternary plots,
    clr-biplots), and permutational MANOVA with pairwise post-hoc tests.
    Developed as supplementary material for the Journal of Microscopy.
